Decision

The new backup brain should not be another browser key path and should not keep living under KaixuSuper-IDE or SkyDex. It should become a dedicated server-side worker package under:

/workspaces/SkyeCDE/Skye0s-s0l26/Sky0s-Platforms/0megaSkyeGate/0megaSkyeGate-BackUP-Brain

That worker should expose the same normalized request and response contract already described in SuperIDE/docs/BACKUP_BRAIN_MIGRATION_STANDARD.md, and 0megaSkyeGate-The-Actual-Gate should treat it as a registered secondary brain instead of leaving backup behavior scattered across unrelated apps.

