Bottom line

The current "backup brain via API key" is not one single thing. It is split across:
- one old direct-provider worker
- one direct OpenAI Netlify function
- several browser-held key flows

The clean path is to make 0megaSkyeGate-BackUP-Brain the only dedicated backup runtime, then point those older surfaces at it and let the main 0mega gate own the brain registry and token issuance.

